```cron
@reboot   command    # run once at startup
@hourly   command    # 0 * * * *
@daily    command    # 0 0 * * *
@weekly   command    # 0 0 * * 0
@monthly  command    # 0 0 1 * *
@yearly   command    # 0 0 1 1 *
```
**Special strings** are shortcuts for common schedules. `@reboot` is particularly useful for startup tasks.
